title: Notice of Special Council Meeting - 27 October 2015 (Wanneroo City Council)
text: ( Source : Wanneroo City Council ) Would you like to contribute to your local community and be part of the decision making process? Why not nominate for one of the City 's committees or working groups. Nominations close 9 October 2015 .More
